summary: Special K Diet Last Week Results
title: Special K Diet Last Week Results
body:
Damaging final week outcomes of the Special K Diet brings in the next weight-loss obstacle. The ViSalus Body by Vi 90 Day Challenge, new to the UK.

Preliminary weigh-in for the Special K Challenge was 14st 2lb

By the end of week 1 weight had increased to 14st 6lb

After re-evaluating the section size week 2 finished 14st 2lb

Generally if an individual was to stick rigidly to the portion dimension mentioned by Kellogg’s Special K it could be feasible to slim down.
